name: Lakshmi Hi-Tech Rubber Industry
overview:
Lakshmi Hi Tech Rubber Industry India Private Limited was established in the year 2012. We have our head office in Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu. Lakshmi Hi Tech Rubber Industry is a registered private limited firm. ]

Our Product Range: Custom Rubber Bands Nylon Rubber Bands Center Line Rubber Bands Craft Rubber Bands Packaging Rubber Bands Wrapping Rubber Bands Natural Rubber Bands Rubber Bands

Our Infrastructure: We are the leading manufacturers and suppliers of quality products that are best to use industrial and domestic purposes rubber bands. These rubber bands go through a rigorous quality checking process before going to the customer end.

Our Quality: If you are searching a company who makes high quality and long lasting products then we are the answer to your search as we promise to provide a wide range and excellent quality and domestic and industrial purposes rubber bands.

Our Clients: Our clients play a vital role in the success of our organization. We choose the top most s in the market and we feel very proud to say that really we have the top most dealers of this business and they have helped us in a large extent to make our clients satisfied and happy by delivering them excellent quality products.

Why Us? What makes us distinguished from others is our quality of providing products of excellent quality, durable, long lasting and wide range of products. We offer easy modes of payment to our customers so that they can pay according to their ease.
